name: Fagocitar-me
description:
"Phagocytize-me"
 
From the series "Mutations", I painted this work some time ago; it belongs to one of the six parts that are exhibited together, but each one, in turn, works independently. The fourth of those six, which is one of my favorites. I think this is one of the most abstract pieces of the whole series. Almost abstract, almost animal.

Oil on Canvas. 
Dimensions: 2126 x 1702 px
Size: 30 x 24 cm.
